title: Celebrity Gossip-Frankie Jonas Star Struck
description: Frankie Jonas is no stranger to hanging out with famous people, but he was shocked when Joe started bringing Sophie Turner to family functions. And Lady Gaga had to postpone her last tour due to health issues, and she gave an update on how she is feeling as her “Chromatica” tour gets rolling.
